{"tid":2188081,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"臨收檔去食碗譚仔","createTime":"2020-09-04T04:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T10:14:26.000Z","uid":179367,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e67a32f01c4543db1032f7e73a373bed48d35103","tid":2188081,"uid":179367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:35:29.000Z","msg":"臨收工終於停雨，又濕又熱，諗住去譚仔食個快嘅，嘆嘆冷氣，飲杯凍嘢。一坐底，唔洗撚叫咗碗物演重慶小辣。<br />\n<br />\n阿姐：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿姐望住我<br />\n阿姐：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我睥返佢<br />\n心諗，做乜歐？<br />\n<br />\n阿姐：仲有茅其他？<br />\n我：aii ，俾杯水我<br />\n阿姐：<br />\n<br />\n.......<br />\n.......<br />\n.......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我：唔該。<br />\n<br />\n叫完嘢食，我留意到隔離枱坐咗對清潔工，一個阿伯一個阿姐，枱上有兩碗過橋米線套餐，兩杯凍檸茶加碟大土匪。<br />\n<br />\n心諗，都啱，食飽啲。<br />\n<br />\n可能趕住6點前收工，好快我碗線同杯熱水就上枱，我飲啖水，食擔米，一邊聽佢地呻吓返工啲同事幾陰濕，新嚟阿邊個邊個有幾卸膊。<br />\n<br />\n我諗起王苑之，都好耐無聽過佢唱歌啦。<br />\n<br />\n阿伯講到火火地滾：最多咪唔撈，等份糧洗咩我？我層樓收租都萬4一個月啦。<br />\n<br />\n 「啪」<br />\n<br />\n佢一嘢拍落張枱到，果吓其實又唔算大聲嘅，但就拍到我應一應。我食粒墨丸，都係激鬼氣，我假假地都係濕鳩degree仔，月入都有萬7一個月啊。<br />\n<br />\n我：靚女寫嘢。<br />\n阿姐：腰乜？<br />\n我：要碟土匪。<br />\n阿姐：要大定細？<br />\n我：aiii ，俾碟大啊。<br />\n阿姐落完單諗住走，但我諗咗一唸，我叫住佢。<br />\n<br />\n我：都係細啊，加多杯凍水得唔得？<br />\n阿姐：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完，走人。<br />\n<br />\n利申：其實譚仔都唔係咁好食姐"},{"pid":"347217dd749547e5fbc5bb79acba1accad787d29","tid":2188081,"uid":217641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:36:51.000Z","msg":"有無問你睇唔睇電視?"},{"pid":"6480740d747bee49c1bb042c5874e0442e708d34","tid":2188081,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7093af4ca89c6fc08e2c2bf4f6975fa912e1a47","tid":2188081,"uid":59929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:41:20.000Z","msg":"ON9故"},{"pid":"7eecd38f38ce35c878ba275996cb54b4fa7ddc02","tid":2188081,"uid":96941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:03:44.000Z","msg":"領悟左唔少道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0a3efdfda4e5b660a9e058ad1dc9c3e327ac72","tid":2188081,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"原來我幽默感係中上，多謝樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"716fccbcf1506d48493cde8e03deed231dc6fcdb","tid":2188081,"uid":179367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b7093af4ca89c6fc08e2c2bf4f6975fa912e1a47","tid":2188081,"uid":59929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T04:41:20.000Z","msg":"ON9故"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:12:25.000Z","msg":"多謝支持"},{"pid":"3158c769374a5e6a2e4e410b426996e01f0d0d31","tid":2188081,"uid":179367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7eecd38f38ce35c878ba275996cb54b4fa7ddc02","tid":2188081,"uid":96941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:03:44.000Z","msg":"領悟左唔少道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:12:45.000Z","msg":"一日領悟咗一年嘅量"},{"pid":"55c87ec6d9aceb9c4ef459019692f7eec4b9d864","tid":2188081,"uid":179367,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a0a3efdfda4e5b660a9e058ad1dc9c3e327ac72","tid":2188081,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:10:15.000Z","msg":"原來我幽默感係中上，多謝樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T05:13:05.000Z","msg":"你自己嘅本事嚟 <br />\n唔洗多謝"},{"pid":"3ed72fa871b1446ef1b1c1ec196f3544eecbc15d","tid":2188081,"uid":192327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0